dc_title_s: Fuel Rank: Russian River Basin, California, 2000-2001
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile shows fuel rankings based on expects fire behavior for unique combinations of topography and vegetative fuels under a given severe weather condition (wind speed, humidity, and temperature).This layer can be used to identify and prioritize pre-fire projects that reduce costs and losses from large fire events.
